body.name: DYRABREST 6-Tire Rotating Bookshelf Floor Standing Bookcase Storage Rack Revolving Book Shelf Tower for Books/CDs, Wood Book Organizer Shelves for Living Room, Book Shop, Office
features: Quality Material: It is made of high-quality New Zealand pine wood, which is strong, durable, and hard-wearing to guarantee a long service life. Meanwhile, It is paint-free and environmentally friendly that does not release harmful substances or gases, making it friendly for families with young children.

Large Storage Space: With 6 tiers and 4 compartments on each tier, Layer Height: 31cm/12.2in, this shelf makes great use of every inch of space for books and other items. The top can also be used for potted plants, dolls, flower pots, or other items to decorate your room and improve space utilization.

Exquisite Workmanship: This bookcase is meticulously polished without burrs to prevent your hands from being scratched, so you can use it with confidence.This bookshelf has raised support legs at the bottom to protect it from moisture and to make it convenient to clean the underside of the shelf.
Strong Load-bearing Capacity: The thickened wood panels(0.47in) are not easily deformed or broken, ensuring a strong load-bearing capacity of up to 110lbs per layer for your daily needs.

Application: This bookshelf can be used for storing books, precious souvenirs, displays, miniature potted plants, photo frames, and other items. It is ideal for corridors, balconies, living rooms, study rooms, bedrooms, nurseries, children's rooms, and other places.
body.description: Description The stacking of your child's thick books one on top of the other on the desk is a huge nuisance and even affects the child's motivation to read. A practical and innovative bookshelf will be an essential addition to your home. You can't go wrong with this rotating bookshelf. Its large space can also be used for small ornaments, greenery, toys, etc., making reading even more fun. It will give your child a happy reading childhood!Key FeaturesEasy to Clean: The surface of this product is polished smooth and flat, making it easy to clean. You can easily wipe off the dust on it with a damp rag.Special Design: This bookshelf has raised support legs at the bottom to protect it from moisture and to make it convenient to clean the underside of the shelf.Convenient to Use: This bookshelf is rotatable and also features an open design, making it easy for you to choose, access, and place your books conveniently and practically.Beautiful Appearance: This minimalist bookshelf has a clear wood grain surface and soft natural tones, which is atmospheric and beautiful, making it an ideal decorative piece for your home.Space Saving: It has a small footprint and makes good use of vertical space. It can be easily accommodated in just a small corner to create a reading corner.Good Organiser: With its sorted storage, you can say goodbye to a messy room as it is well organized. It will also help your child to develop good storage habits from an early age.Free Assembly: This rotating bookcase has six tiers, which can be assembled as you wish to make 1, 2, 3, 4 or 5 tiers of shelves.DetailsReinforced Rotating Chassis: The bottom stainless steel chassis uses steel ball bearings for a stable center of gravity and a smooth, non-jamming rotation, giving you a better user experience.Curved Baffle: Each compartment has been thoughtfully designed with a baffle to prevent items from falling out. Its curved corners are polished smooth to prevent your hands from being scratched.SpecificationNumber of Tiers: 6Assembly Requirement: YesInstallation Type: FreestandingShape: CylindricalMaterial: Pine WoodColor: WoodBoard Thickness: 12mm/0.47inLayer Height: 31cm/12.2inSupport Leg Height: 10cm/3.93inDiameter: 46cm/18.11inPacking Size: 52*52*12cm/20.47*20.47*4.72inGross Weight: 18kg/39.68lbsEach Layer Weight Capacity: 50kg/110lbsPackage Included1* Rotating Bookshelf
